 documentation/Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md  |  2 +-
 .../Quickstart-on-how-to-write-tests.md       | 27 +++++++++----------
 .../resolve-pnpm-lock-merge-conflict.md       |  2 +-
 3 files changed, 15 insertions(+), 16 deletions(-)

